./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:184:### Feature 3 — Live Stream + Archive at cypherclaw.holdenu.com
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:186:**Aesthetic spec:** See `cypherclaw-v2-design-statement-2026-05-22.md` §1, §6.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:189:- **Encoding (on cypherclaw):** `audio_streamer.py` daemon subscribes to JACK output bus, runs Opus encoding via `pyogg` or shells `opusenc`/`ffmpeg`. Produces 6-second Opus segments at ~96 kbps. Each segment HTTP-POSTed to the Cloudflare Worker.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:190:- **Segment/playlist management (Cloudflare Worker, extends existing holdenu-api worker):**
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:191:  - `POST /api/cypherclaw/segment` — receives a binary segment + metadata header (sequence number, duration, current scene, current tuning). Stores in R2 under `cypherclaw/live/{YYYY-MM-DD}/seg-{seq}.opus`. Updates `live.m3u8` HLS playlist (last ~10 segments).
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:192:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/live.m3u8` — serves current playlist (no auth).
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:193:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/segment/{path}` — serves segment from R2 with byte-range support.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:194:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/live-features` — Server-Sent Events stream of live audio features + scene metadata + current tuning. cypherclaw POSTs periodically to a feature-update endpoint; Worker fans out via Durable Object.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:195:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/sessions` — JSON list of archived sessions with metadata.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:196:  - `GET /api/cypherclaw/sessions/{session_id}` — JSON detail with title (per CypherClaw's naming pattern), date, dominant house, dominant tuning, MIDI-influence list, duration, segment URLs.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:197:- **Session archival:** When the composer transitions out of a long "session" (definition TBD by engineering; suggest: a continuous span >= 8 minutes with reasonable rms variance), `session_archiver.py` selects representative segments, concatenates into a single Opus file, computes the title per CypherClaw's pattern (`{House-Imagery} / {Tuning-Character} — {DD Month}`), uploads to R2 under `cypherclaw/archive/{session_id}/`, and records metadata.
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:198:- **Page (`cypherclaw.holdenu.com`):** Static page served by Cloudflare Worker or Pages. HTML structure:
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:200:  - Background: a slowly-cycling layer of GlyphWeave images (pulled from `cypherclaw:8080/gallery` exported by another sprint task)
./sdp/cypherclaw-v2-analysis/prd-snapshot.md:203:- **DNS / TLS:** New Cloudflare DNS A/AAAA records for `cypherclaw.holdenu.com` → Worker route. Reuse existing Cloudflare zone.
