./sdp/prd-cypherclaw-v2-2026-05-22.md:205:- `catalog-explorer/pages/cypherclaw/visualizer.js` (canvas visualizer)
./sdp/prd-cypherclaw-v2-2026-05-22.md:206:- `catalog-explorer/pages/cypherclaw/styles.css` (page styling)
