docs/master-plan-20260409.md:3:Four systems need work in the right order: **CypherClaw** (art organism), **PromptClaw** (toolkit/dev), **sdp-cli** (core pipeline), **R750** (work deployment). This document sequences all of them to avoid thrashing, blocked dependencies, or duplicated effort.
