+# Task T-054a: Live MIDI WebSocket Room Bootstrap
+
+## Problem Statement
+
+T-053 begins publishing live MIDI events toward the holdenu Cloudflare Worker,
+and T-054 requires a Durable Object backed `/api/cypherclaw/live-midi`
